Messages.Value: Thank you for calling our travel agency, my name is Isabella Taylor. How may I assist you today?
Hi Isabella, my name is Jane Smith and I am calling about a recent trip I took to New York City.
Hi Jane, I'm sorry to hear that you had an issue with your trip to New York City. What seems to be the problem?
Well, I flew in from Chicago last Tuesday and my luggage never arrived. It's been over a week now and I still haven't received any information about where my bags are.
I'm so sorry to hear that Jane. Let me see what I can do to assist you. Can you please provide me with your flight information and reservation number?
Sure, I flew with American Airlines on flight AA345 and my reservation number is 123456789.
Thank you for the information Jane. I will contact American Airlines and try to locate your bags. Can you please provide me with your contact information so I can follow up with you?
Yes, my phone number is 555-555-5555 and my email is jane.smith@email.com.
Thank you, Jane. I will reach out to you as soon as I have an update on your bags. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all. Thank you for your help, Isabella.
